      "rationale": "Eleven non-cannulated 7.5 mm pedicle screw constructs assembled from a single production lot. Five constructs tested at Lab A (FDA), six at Lab B (DePuy Synthes). Coefficient of variation in stiffness across labs < 4%, confirming sample representativeness."
