      "rationale": "Testing performed under a single ASTM F1717 standard load configuration at quasi-static rate only. A second load rate or fixture offset condition was not available within project scope. This factor is below the required level; risk accepted given that F1717 is a standardised protocol and the single condition aligns directly with the COU loading scenario."
