    "rationale": "Twelve of thirteen V&V 40 credibility factors meet or exceed the required level. The single below-threshold factor (Test conditions, achieved 2 vs. required 3) is confined to the absence of a second load rate; all three QoIs pass quantitative acceptance criteria with E/uval well below 1.96 and relative differences below 2%. The overall evidence body is judged sufficient to support use of the FEA framework for regulatory submission. Package conforms to ProfileMinimal; digital signature is pending the organisation's signature workflow and will be applied prior to formal submission.",
